file.name: fuyuko-openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: fuyuko-be
  description: fuyuko be api
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https'
components:
  schemas:
    ApiResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        messages:
          type: array
          items:
            type: object
            properties:
              status:
                type: string
                enum: [INFO, WARN, ERROR, SUCCESS]
              message:
                type: string
    ApiResponse2:
      allOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ApiResponse'
      properties:
        payload:
          type: object
          properties:
            test:
              type: string
  responses:
    GenericResponse:
      description: ''
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ApiResponse'
paths:
  /v1/api/view/{viewId}/category/{categoryId}:
    delete:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: viewId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
          description: View ID
        - in: path
          name: categoryId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
          description: Category ID
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/GenericResponse'
  /v1/api/data-export-artifact/{dataExportArtifactId}:
    delete:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: dataExportArtifactId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/GenericResponse'
  /v1/api/view/{viewId}/user/{userId}/remove-favourite-items:
    delete:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: viewId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
        - in: path
          name: userId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/GenericResponse'
  /v1/api/view/{itemId}/image/{itemImageId}:
    delete:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: itemId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
        - in: path
          name: itemImageId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/GenericResponse'
  /v1/api/view/{viewId}/custom-rules:
    delete:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: viewId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            minimum: 1
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/GenericResponse'
